DISPLAY MACRO MSG 
 LEA DX,MSG 
 MOV AH,09H 
INT 21H
 ENDM
 DATA SEGMENT
 STR DB ‘RACECAR’ 
 LEN DW LEN-STR 
 REV DB LEN-STR DUP(0) 
 MSG1 DB 'STRING IS PALINDROME$' 
 MSG2 DB 'STRING IS NOT PALINDROME$' 
 DATA ENDS
 ASSUME CS:CODE, DS:DATA
 CODE SEGMENT
 START: MOV AX,DATA 
 MOV DS,AX 
 MOV ES,AX 
 LEA SI,LEN-1 
 LEA DI,REV 
 MOV CX,LEN 
 BACK: MOV AL,[SI] 
 MOV [DI],AL 
 DEC SI 
 INC DI 
 LOOP BACK 
 CLD 
LEA SI,STR 
 LEA DI,REV 
 MOV CX,LEN 
REPE CMPSB 
 JE PALIN 
 DISPLAY MSG2 
 JMP QUIT 
 PALIN: DISPLAY MSG1 
 QUIT: MOV AH,4CH 
 INT 21H
 CODE ENDS
 END START
